What makes popular or ranked better?

You rank your candidates. Then all the votes are counted. Did any candidate get a majority of the counted votes? If not, then eliminate the lowest-scoring candidate and give their votes to the next highest choice of each of their voters. Then repeat until someone has a majority. Ensures that spoiler candidates don't spoil races
